FuncDef: This command excludes IPv4 prefix(es) from anip-prefix-list.Theprefix-excludecommand is mutually exclusive withapply-path.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies a valid IPv4 address prefix in dotted decimal notation. Values-0.0.0.0 to 255.255.255.255 (host bit must be 0).
Specifies the length of the entered IPv4 prefix. Values-0 to 32.
